{
  "texts": [
    "4.2 TRACKING INFORMATION FLOW THROUGH DEPTH",
    "At each layer ℓ we track two complementary, operational quantities: task signal via linear probe accuracy on [CLS], and input-like structure by reconstructing pre-PE embeddings z 0 from patch tokens.",
    "These are not mutual informations in the information-theoretic sense, but the performance of specific decoders that serve as probes into what the representation makes linearly accessible."
  ]
}